  "invariants": [
    "OS autonomy is bounded local supervision, not unrestricted action",
    "boot success does not imply truth authority",
    "module PASS is evidence only and remains candidate-level",
    "module failure enters HOLD by default",
    "state checkpoint records kernel state but does not overwrite semantic memory",
    "audit events are append-only JSONL receipts with hash-chain continuity",
    "external API calls are not required for the kernel",
